                    <h1 class="domdom">18</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1451">Riding Along (2009)</a></h1>

                    <h2>18 Jul 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Hitchhiking across Europe, from one meeting to another,with an old mechanical 16mm camera and a sound recorder,the author takes us on a journey with no destination.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1451">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

