                    <h1 class="domdom">23</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1441">Academic Film Center Of Belgrade Presents</a></h1>

                    <h2>23 Jul 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Collection of short films from Academic
Film Center of Belgrade, established 1958 as a cinema club for
film amateurs, since it has produced over 500 films.
It also hosts two film festivals - Alternative
Film/Video and European Animated Film Festival Balkanima. </p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1441">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

                </section>
