                    <h1 class="domdom">24</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1442">Independent Film Center Vorky Team Of Ruma Presents</a></h1>

                    <h2>24 Jul 2014, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Vorky
Team was established in Ruma 2005 in memory of
Serbo-American film artist Slavko Vorkapich. The Team organizes
screenings and debates, but also produces films and hosts the
International Festival of One Minute Film Mister Vorky. </p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1442">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

