                    <h1 class="domdom">12</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1594">Alternative Film/Video Festival 2014 (Various)</a></h1>

                    <h2>12 Feb 2015, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Showcasing the 2014 jury selection from Alternative Film/Video Festival. Hailing from Belgrade, Serbia the festival has specialized in alternative/experimental films from all over the world. It's been running from 1982-1990 and 2003-present, missing over a decade due to a war.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1594">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

