                    <h1 class="domdom">18</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1593">Balkanima - European Animation Film Festival (Various)</a></h1>

                    <h2>18 Feb 2015, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>An eclectic program from Balkanima - animation short film festival based in Belgrade, Serbia. The festival endorses European animation and have specialized in shorts coming from the Southeast Europe and Balkans; a rare treat around here! </p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/1593">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

